item.title: Loose Change
item.dc:creator: @irfan786 irfan786
item.description:
@irfan786 wrote:

[quote=“LordDrakiss, post:24, topic:15121”]forgive my limitted knowledge, not that the goverment would EVER lie to it’s citizens, but jet fuel doesn’t burn hot enough to melt steal, but there was melted steal it the basment, concrete was found 5 miles away, but the impact was inward… all the black boxes were non-recoverable, but they got all of the ID’s intact ? the hole in the outside of the Pentagon is round… where is the wing impact ? there were no plane hull pieces in the aftermath footage of the pentagon, the interior damage was larger than the outside damage, the hole was as small as a single engine plane, but supposedly was a much larger passenger plane, the so-called pilot would have had to bring the plane in (A passenger plane no less) at 6 inches above the ground while going AROUND trees to impact at that point, but the man they SAY piloted the plane had an instructor that said “it’s no suprise to me he crashed, he couldn’t land in the ocean without missing his mark.” Islam teaches that if you kill another believer of the faith you will burn in eternal damnation, there was a day care and mosque (Muslim church) in the towers, the claim about why the towers collapsed INWARD and DOWN, was that the fire so weakend the supports that the top fell in crushing it beneath it’s own weight, but the other towers top had already fallen and both towers were of course designed to hold that much weight, if anything like that had happened it should have happend both slower and toppled outward… building seven is never reference, it was a nearby building that went down at exactly the same time as the other two… 5 blocks away, later when it came up, congress declared that it was a coincidental demolition at the exact time. in a congressional hearing the investigative commity was charged with submitting false information and public pergury by 3 different senators when information conflicted openly. evidence showed that when the hijacked plan was called in the air strike was ordered to fly 500 miles in the opposite direction to practice manuvers.

as I said, I’m no expert, and I’d never accuse the goverment of intentionally lying to us…
and there is all sorts of other factual congressionally recorded material you can get on this.

LordDrakiss - laughing[/quote]
That was hard to read but I got it.
Pretty interesting facts you pointed out, will check later if their true or not.
